  "text": "In this case, the full theory, i.e., the bulk theory plus domain wall CFT, respects background diffeomorphism symmetry. This cancellation of the CFT gravitational anomaly by the bulk is an example of Callan-Harvey anomaly inflow [CITATION_1] .",
